        "image_with_text_kPhgQj": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_is_LGD.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A Lab Grown Diamond is a real diamond. Created in advanced laboratories using innovative technology, these gems are optically, chemically, and physically identical to mined diamonds. The only difference is their origin.<br/>Lab diamonds are grown through processes</p>",
