        "rich_text_8zQCTn": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>from mining or conflict. Every gem represents innovation, responsibility, and respect for the planet. Moissanite is also lab-created but doesn’t hold the same legacy or certification standards as diamonds.</p><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>, we believe brilliance should never come at the planet’s expense. Choosing a lab-grown diamond means embracing a sustainable future without compromising on luxury.</p>",
