            "content": "<p>For engagement rings, anniversaries, or heirloom pieces, lab-grown diamonds offer the authenticity, value, and timeless charm that moissanite simply can’t match.</p><p>Lucira’s expert gemologists can help you select the perfect diamond that aligns with your values and vision.</p>",
