            "faq_question": "5. Do moissanite or lab diamonds lose their sparkle over time?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Neither loses brilliance when cared for properly. However, moissanite may accumulate surface oil or dirt more easily, which can dull its shine until cleaned. Lab-grown diamonds maintain their brilliance for a lifetime.</p>"
